# dealloc()

**Instance Method**

Deallocates the memory occupied by the receiver.

## Declaration

```swift
func dealloc()
```

## Discussion

This method behaves as described in the `NSObject` class specification under the [doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/ObjectiveC/NSObject-swift.class/dealloc] instance method.

## Related Documentation

- **finalize()**: The garbage collector invokes this method on the receiver before disposing of the memory it uses.
